# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and set values for your environment.
# https://vite.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html
#
# QA checklist (dataset upload, remote API): docs/testing-plan-dataset-upload.md

# Backend origin for API calls. Default when unset: `/api` (Vite dev server proxies to :8000).
# For a remote API or `vite preview`, set the full origin (https://...) and add it to
# PYPEDEID_CORS_ORIGINS on the API. Large JSONL: raise PYPEDEID_MAX_BODY_BYTES or you get 413.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Sent as `X-API-Key` on every request. Required when the API has
# PYPEDEID_ADMIN_API_KEYS / PYPEDEID_INFERENCE_API_KEYS configured.
# Use an **admin**-scoped key for the Playground (Datasets, eval, transform, **Upload JSONL**).
# GET /health (optional) can return api_key_scope so UIs know admin vs inference for the key you send.
# VITE_API_KEY=
